& [ClaimTypeSet] is the inventory vocabulary
  + [formal_math_claim] is a claim about a standard mathematical object or theorem
  + [symbolic_interpretation_claim] is a metaphor or narrative model claim using resonance, curvature, memory, collapse, phase, or field language
  + [computational_model_claim] is a claim about an experiment, instrument, state, update, or measurable symbolic process
  + [cross_problem_transfer_claim] is a claim that one problem's symbolic structure implies insight for another
  + [proof_status_claim] is a statement about solved/open/proved status
  + [outside_or_gap] is a claim lacking formal bridge to proof authority

